product_name: 25.5-cu ft Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Ice Maker (EasyCare Stainless Steel)
description: This Lowe's Exclusive Frigidaire 25.5 cu. Ft. Side-by-side refrigerator is similar to FFSS2615TS but has an EasyCare™ Stainless Steel finish that resists fingerprints and is easy to clean. Additionally, it has a large capacity and makes it easy to stay organized with gallon door storage and Crisper Drawers for fruits and vegetables. PureSource 3 filtration gives you great-tasting clean water and ice. Bright Lighting in both the refrigerator and freezer compartments makes it easy to see what's inside.

product_name: Pur Bark Gray Full Murphy Bed
description: Combining style and convenience, Pur by Bestar is the perfect solution to furnished condos, lofts, studios, guest’s rooms and home offices. The collection brings multi functionality to a single room. The mechanism provides simplified assembly of the Wall Bed. Increased comfort due to Euroslat mattress support system. Simple and safe dual piston system makes opening and closing user-friendly. Easy to use; use the handle to pull the bed towards you to lower the bed and flip the leg down onto the floor. The bed when opened will require a clearance of 85. 3“ from the wall extending into the room. The minimum height required of the ceiling is 861/4 in. Clearance of 9. 6“ under the bed when it is open. Mattress not included. Accommodates most standard Full mattresses.  The mattress must meet the following requirements:Thickness between 20. 3 and 25. 4 cm (8 and 10 in). Weight between 27. 2 and 40. 8 kg (60 and 90 lb). Size of  190. 5 cm (L) x 137 cm (W) (75 x 54 in). No futons. Box spring not required. Shaker-inspired trim and metal handles on wall bed. Assembly required. Easy to install.
